oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Spring Activity Banquet
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Activities; Events; Banquets; De La Salle Christian Brothers; Teachers; Students; Mothers
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Christian Brothers community members gather for a spring banquet served by The Mothers Club, presided over by Mrs. John Farrell. Included in the photograph are Brother I. Francis, Brother John Chrysostom, Brother J. Arthur Higgins, Brother Hilary Eugene, Brother Henry William, Brother J. Ambrose, and Coach Shelby Schneider. Champions honored include football players, basketball players, wrestlers, boxers, and tennis players.
